Geoje Yaho.

339
00:13:49,795 --> 00:13:52,064
Kkuh-jeeek... Eeyaaah-hong.

340
00:13:52,064 --> 00:13:54,667
Geoje yaaang-hooong.

341
00:13:54,667 --> 00:13:56,468
Ể? Sai cả rồi thì phải.

342
00:13:56,468 --> 00:13:57,503
